    <item>
      <title>Generating Specs via AI from Source Code: When AI Analyzes Your Codebase to Create Realistic Specifications</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/specifications/2026/01/23/ai-specs-generation-source-code.html</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Jan 2026 09:00:00 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/specifications/2026/01/23/ai-specs-generation-source-code.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;url: /specifications/2026/01/23/ai-specs-generation-source-code.html&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;add-multi-factor-authentication&#34;&gt;&amp;ldquo;Add Multi-Factor Authentication&amp;rdquo;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monday morning. Release planning meeting.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Product Manager: &amp;ldquo;For the next release, we&amp;rsquo;re adding multi-factor authentication. It&amp;rsquo;s a priority customer request.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The PM opens Notion and starts writing the spec:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-markdown&#34; data-lang=&#34;markdown&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;# Capability: Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;**Objective:**&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Allow users to secure their accounts with multiple authentication methods.&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;**Supported methods:**&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; SMS with 6-digit code&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; Authenticator app (TOTP)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; Hardware security key (FIDO2)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; Email with confirmation link&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;**User Stories:**&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; As a user, I want to enable MFA in my settings&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; As a user, I want to choose my preferred method&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; As a user, I want to configure multiple backup methods&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;PM: &amp;ldquo;Spec done. Estimate?&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
